# -*- mode: conf; -*-

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User lunaryorn@gmail.com
PassCmd "imap-pass lunaryorn@gmail.com"
UseIMAPS yes
RequireSSL yes
UseTLSv1.2 yes

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Documents/Mail/
Inbox ~/Documents/Mail/Inbox
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Master :gmail:
Slave :local:
Patterns * "![Google Mail]/*" "[Google Mail]/Drafts" "[Google Mail]/Sent Mail" "[Google Mail]/Starred" "[Google Mail]/Trash"
Create Slave
Expunge Both
Sync All
